
Goals for next release:
-----------------------

* Add a dialog class

* Add support for native dialogs (e.g. file dialogs)

* Add basic support for defaults

* Add support for the border property

* Add a structured testing framework

* Add documentation (including major docstrings)

* Add support for the document/view model

Longer term goals:
------------------

* Add full menu system

* Add full event system

* Add advanced support for default, including default
  "shrink-wrapping" of windows and frames that aren't
  given an explicit size

* Support accessibility standards
